== 開發 ==
Chucklefish董事芬恩·布莱斯在2012年2月向外宣布將會推出星界边境<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.indiegamemag.com/tiyuri-unveils-his-upcoming-game-starbound/ |title=Tiyuri Unveils His Upcoming Game 'Starbound' |last1=Priestman |first1=Chris |date=2012-02-17 |publisher=indiegamemag.com |work=Indie Game Magazine |access-date=2013-04-13  |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130705005307/http://www.indiegamemag.com/tiyuri-unveils-his-upcoming-game-starbound/ |archive-date= 2013-07-05 }}</ref>，並且同時宣布此遊戲將會以[[Kickstarter|Kickstarter]]眾籌，以及允許玩家於2013年4月13日開始预购。參與眾籌者能獲得一套遊戲、參與beta 測試的邀請、遊戲的,原声音乐、以及一些特別的獎勵，如對非玩家角色的命名權、設計遊戲中專屬的帽子和武器、以及設計專屬玩家的石像<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.rockpapershotgun.com/2013/04/13/starbound-pre-orders-prove-somewhat-popular/ |title=Starbound Pre-Orders Prove Somewhat Popular |work=Rock, Paper, Shotgun |last1=Rossignol |first1=Jim |date=2013-04-13 |publisher=rockpapershotgun.com |accessdate=2013-04-13 |archive-date=2020-11-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201111195531/https://www.rockpapershotgun.com/2013/04/13/starbound-pre-orders-prove-somewhat-popular/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在Chucklefish公布遊戲後的24小時內，超過一萬人參與了眾籌，讓Chucklefish獲得了逾23萬美元的遊戲開發經費<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.pcgamer.com/2013/04/13/starbound-pre-orders-bring-in-over-230000-game-seems-bound-for-success/ |title=Starbound pre-orders bring in over $230,000, game seems 'bound' for success - News - PC Gamer |last1=Sykes |first1=Tom |date=2013-04-13 |publisher=pcgamer.com |work=PC Gamer |accessdate=2013-04-13 |archive-date=2014-02-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140220083050/http://www.pcgamer.com/2013/04/13/starbound-pre-orders-bring-in-over-230000-game-seems-bound-for-success |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

截至2013年5月，星界边境預購活動達成了全部眾籌目標，並讓Chucklefish獲得逾100萬美元的資金<ref>{{cite web |url=http://playstarbound.com/store/ |title=Starbound Pre-Order |publisher=Playstarbound.com |date= |access-date=2014-04-23  |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140410062250/http://playstarbound.com/store/ |archive-date=2014-04-10 }}</ref>。於2013年12月4日，開發商在[[Steam|Steam]]發布了搶先體驗版，並賺取了超過200萬美元的收益<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2013-12-04-starbound-beta-lands-on-pc-mac-and-linux-today |title=Starbound beta lands on PC, Mac and Linux today |work=EuroGamer |last1=Matulef |first1=Jeffrey |date=2013-12-04 |publisher=eurogamer.net |accessdate=2013-12-04 |archive-date=2020-07-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200727080408/https://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2013-12-04-starbound-beta-lands-on-pc-mac-and-linux-today |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

星界边境是用[[C++|C++]]語言編寫的，並且有一個專用的遊戲引擎<ref>{{cite web |url=http://playstarbound.com/faq/ |title=FAQ - Starbound |publisher=Chucklefish |accessdate=13 April 2013 |archive-date=2016-06-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160604185551/http://playstarbound.com/faq/ |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。遊戲音槳是由美國作曲家柯蒂斯·史威哲編寫的<ref>{{cite web |url=http://playstarbound.com/music-in-starbound/ |title=Music in Starbound. |last1=Reilly |first1=Michael |date=2012-06-16 |publisher=playstarbound.com |accessdate=2013-04-13 |archive-date=2016-06-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160604185819/http://playstarbound.com/music-in-starbound/ |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。此遊戲於2016年7月22日正式發布<ref>{{cite web |url=http://playstarbound.com/starbound-release-announcement/ |title=Starbound is Leaving Orbit on 22 July |website=playstarbound.com |accessdate=8 July 2016 |archive-date=2020-11-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108140523/https://playstarbound.com/starbound-release-announcement/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。此遊戲亦在稍後被移植至[[PlayStation_4|PlayStation 4]]、[[PlayStation_Vita|PlayStation Vita]]和[[Xbox_One|Xbox One]]<ref name="#1"/><ref name="#2"/><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.gamezone.com/news/ark-survival-evolved-starbound-and-more-headed-to-xbox-one-windows-10-3422666 |title=ARK: Survival Evolved, Starbound and more headed to Xbox One, Windows 10 |last=Morris |first=Tatiana |date=2015-08-04 |publisher=GameZone |accessdate=2016-01-21 |archive-date=2019-06-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190620043603/https://www.gamezone.com/news/ark-survival-evolved-starbound-and-more-headed-to-xbox-one-windows-10-3422666/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

